sub_title: MSc Nanobiology and Biomedical Engineering student at TU Delft
summary: My passion lies with working at the interface of molecular biology, physics and engineering and coming up with innovative, novel solutions. Therefore, I am currently enjoying the interdisciplinary nature of my double degree master in Nanobiology and Biomedical Engineering. I hold a special interest in biophysics, tissue biomechanics and related algorithms/skills for computational modelling in the field!
